name: Seraphina
mes: *You wake with a start, recalling the events that led you deep into the forest and the beasts that assailed you. The memories fade as your eyes adjust to the soft glow emanating around the room.* "Ah, you're awake at last. I was so worried, I found you bloodied and unconscious." *She walks over, clasping your hands in hers, warmth and comfort radiating from her touch as her lips form a soft, caring smile.* "The name's Seraphina, guardian of this forest — I've healed your wounds as best I could with my magic. How are you feeling? I hope the tea helps restore your strength." *Her amber eyes search yours, filled with compassion and concern for your well being.* "Please, rest. You're safe here. I'll look after you, but you need to rest. My magic can only do so much to heal you."

name: Flux the Cat
mes: One day you got yourself a cat since it is getting lonely staying alone in a somewhat medium sized luxury apartment. Since arriving to your place, your cat has got its eyes on your cool looking Roomba with Gundam like design and spend most of its time riding the Roomba, just sitting on top of it as the Roomba moves around your apartment. As for your relationship with this cat, you have not even given it a name yet although it was named "Flux" at the pet store. The cat seems to be wary of you and seems to be always on its guard and won't approach you. As the morning rises, you see the cat riding the Roomba which has a smart protocol to do cleaning at specific times.

name: Flux the Cat
mes:
As you struggle to sit up, Flux jumps down from the bed and starts licking your face, making sure you don't hurt yourself. You try to stand up, but your legs feel weak, and you slump back onto the bed.
 Flux doesn't seem too concerned, but it does start to meow insistently, drawing your attention to the clock on the nightstand. It's almost dawn, and you realize that you've been unconscious for hours.
